{"tid":2260954,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"七成市民反對大灣區港人投票","createTime":"2020-10-28T03:37:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T08:04:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"011d3c37858da5bda845ef12b2a52d6f38b740ad","tid":2260954,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:37:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/B4VAT74VK5FKXHWH34WUJVRZSY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FB4VAT74VK5FKXHWH34WUJVRZSY%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=a046da70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FB4VAT74VK5FKXHWH34WUJVRZSY%2F&h=b2a713f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/B4VAT74VK5FKXHWH34WUJVRZSY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n七成市民反對大灣區港人投票<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JPA3lhxhGAhFkqPvv-UlqrFnvcg=/5627x3751/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QPBPN7LMTBCWBBQDPCMMGWSIO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJPA3lhxhGAhFkqPvv-UlqrFnvcg%3D%2F5627x3751%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQPBPN7LMTBCWBBQDPCMMGWSIO4.jpg&h=1fa7f9f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳家洛<br />\n<br />\n【香港民研】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：林鄭11.3帶五局長上京接旨  免撞五中全會 評論：不懂國情自以為是<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】特首林鄭月娥昨稱正重新檢視內地港人投票政策，但香港民意研究所的民調顯示，近七成受訪者反對大灣區投票，只有近兩成受訪者支持。浸會大學政治國際關係學系副教授、「香港選舉觀察計劃」成員陳家洛直言，林鄭若硬推計劃，只會斷送香港由上世紀80年代起建立的規章制度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中間派反對率達67%<br />\n<br />\n香港民研本月19至22日成功訪問1,020名香港居民，了解是否支持容許內地港人在內地投票，結果多達68%受訪者反對，僅約18%支持；以年齡層劃分，反對者中85%為18至29歲，50歲或以上有61%；18至29歲組別中只有3%支持；50歲或。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：777賴台拒簽證 潘母斥冷漠不仁<br />\n<br />\n陳家洛分析，政府未有充份解答港人憂慮，加上無視選管會早前報告指需研究跨境投票引伸的法律、公平性等問題，反映根本未有。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民調顯示林鄭最新評分只有27.2分，較月初跌1.3分，49%受訪者給予林鄭0分，反對她出任特首比率高達74%，相反支持率僅18%，民。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9705a958a5a3e9a590c0dccb98a1822379a84d3d","tid":2260954,"uid":221343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"林奠話大部份市民支持喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503b8a72701d5b92f702202a477d2abf8c6be028","tid":2260954,"uid":253016,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:38:45.000Z","msg":"700成都冇用"},{"pid":"6ff5e8859306accd0f56181cd58ae53ebb7f3f95","tid":2260954,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"泛民支持者唔計"},{"pid":"f1598dc440a2b1de46959f923897785606cd18ab","tid":2260954,"uid":277339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"反正777睇唔到就即係大家都同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 50歲或以上竟然有61%反對"},{"pid":"5507570aa2b4b5cedf76a2ae745fbb53e8560ebb","tid":2260954,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9bc1371d0c89271705d7037640dead310129c9b","tid":2260954,"uid":53922,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所違反國家法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c2689dd7340cffef80f8fe7079e919553ae85a","tid":2260954,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"鄭月娥當睇唔到"},{"pid":"d5b7642bc2fa30dfde5a78c357b211a89dc09d1c","tid":2260954,"uid":27411,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f1598dc440a2b1de46959f923897785606cd18ab","tid":2260954,"uid":277339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"反正777睇唔到就即係大家都同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h